  • Classes in model used by control

    AccessLevel
    AccessLevel is an Enum to enumerate the hierarchy of access levels particular Users have for particular Conferences.
    Conference
    Conferences store the Conference object's unique ID number, name, the assigned Program Chair, a description of the Conference, the start and end dates of manuscript submission and the Conference itself and the location.
    Manuscript
    Manuscript stores the manuscripts to be submitted to a Conference.
    Review
    Model for the manuscript reviews.
    Status
    Status enumeration gives an intuitive names to the categories of manuscript submission status.
    User
    A class designed to model a user for our conference management system.
